<plot>Though young adult Isaac dreams of exploring the jungles of Bhutan with his love, Sara, Sara's industrialist tycoon father has plans for them to marry and take permanent residence with him in a New York office building. Isaac runs away from the engagement brunch and takes refuge in the fields, forests, and fountains of Central Park. Meanwhile, Isaac's childhood therapist, Dr. Bloore, is in hot pursuit.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?568382</url></doc>
